nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 181 is the 159th issue of the Star Wars Insider magazine and the eighty-ninth issue published by Titan Magazines. It was published on May 29, 2018.

In this issue we celebrate the movie's release with a host of Solo-related features, as well as an interview with comics legend Roy Thomas, who wrote the very Han and Chewie comic strips that sustained my Star Wars obsession way back when.
